text: Eastbourne Carriage Sidings are located in Eastbourne, East Sussex, England, on the East Coastway Line near Eastbourne station. == Present == They provide stabling for Southern Class 377 and 442 EMUs. There is also a carriage cleaning road and an engineers' siding. == References == Category: Railway sidings in England Category:Rail transport in East Sussex
title: Eastbourne Carriage Sidings
